  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2824170/extras/4a1caaafaa7b8f4922bda0a510b7920d.avif?t=1715973468\" width=600 height=500 /></span><br>Alien toddler Jumpy has crashed and needs your help!<br>Join Jumpy on his adventure to recover his UFO wreckage, repair it and return to his home planet. Use tools like the shovel, the metal detector or the hammer and puzzle and jump through an enchanting and cozy world full of floating islands.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2824170/extras/d6962416ecd27ca92133fec9860a38e5.poster.avif?t=1715973468\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2824170/extras/d6962416ecd27ca92133fec9860a38e5.webm?t=1715973468\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2824170/extras/d6962416ecd27ca92133fec9860a38e5.mp4?t=1715973468\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2824170/extras/75a0ab7c2e8b71fbaad5d8b71abdf9c5.poster.avif?t=1715973468\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2824170/extras/75a0ab7c2e8b71fbaad5d8b71abdf9c5.webm?t=1715973468\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2824170/extras/75a0ab7c2e8b71fbaad5d8b71abdf9c5.mp4?t=1715973468\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2824170/extras/4b6318a9a623ad3f886fb60b5ebe0438.avif?t=1715973468\" width=600 height=150 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Master the game through precise, skillful jumping and puzzle solving<br></li><li>Enjoy classic pixel graphics powered by a modern engine<br></li><li>Use tools like the shovel, hammer, metal detector or translocator to progress through the level<br></li><li>Find cosmetic items and change the protagonist’s appearance<br></li><li>Enjoy the cozy and relaxed background music<br></li><li>Show off your jumping skills in Speedrun Mode</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2824170/extras/53b3203329285cad731a86631e5dc17c.poster.avif?t=1715973468\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2824170/extras/53b3203329285cad731a86631e5dc17c.webm?t=1715973468\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2824170/extras/53b3203329285cad731a86631e5dc17c.mp4?t=1715973468\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2824170/extras/e925b70b5bc253319747e885a4e85c99.poster.avif?t=1715973468\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2824170/extras/e925b70b5bc253319747e885a4e85c99.webm?t=1715973468\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2824170/extras/e925b70b5bc253319747e885a4e85c99.mp4?t=1715973468\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2824170/extras/a6da4eb6a2b2fe56e77dbe5f11ff610d.avif?t=1715973468\" width=600 height=150 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_im